details.comment: The code imports necessary modules and sets up a setup script for the "detr" package using setuptools. It defines the package name, version, licenses, and reads the long description from the README file.
details.content:
from distutils.core import setup
from setuptools import find_packages
setup(
    name='detr',
    version='0.0.0',
    packages=find_packages(),
    license='MIT License',
    long_description=open('README.md').read(),
)
